_sText:
My version of the map with breakable cubes. I don't know the original name of the map and can't find it so i just remade it.

It's a small map without much work so i can handle critics.

It is good if you set the gravity of the server to 750 because not anyone is good in jumping on 64x64 boxes.

You can create mapconfigs easily if you create a cfg folder in the map folder of your server and add a .cfg file with the name of the map. With this map the filename must be "fy_cubes.cfg".

Hope you have fun.

Greetz
